text.section:
This title does not apply to:
other than a lease of real estate for the State's use, any real property acquisition by the State, including property subject to condemnation;
settlement of litigation;
except for proceedings to enforce this title, settlement of judicial or administrative enforcement proceedings by or on behalf of the State; and
agreements concerning standards for locating facilities in a State right-of-way when a business entity has a statutory right to be in the right-of-way.
